quotes.quote: Duty is not collective; it is personal.
What is most personal is most universal.
Personal liberty is not personal license.
Personal power is the ability to take action.
Personal love is concentrated universal love.
Your personal truth is your gift to the world.
Memory is the personal journalism of the soul.
The personal is political, but only to a point.
Personal pride is probably a bad guide to merit.
In love, each man is his own personal challenge.
Picture in your mind a sense of personal destiny.
That which is most personal, is most interesting.
Your journey on earth is personal journey of life.
Personal growth is about progress, not perfection.
You are the architect of your personal experience.
Personal chemistry forges the way for musical chemistry.
Personal Vision is often the catalyst for wise decisions.
Personal disintegration remains always an imminent danger.
Art is a personal act of courage.
Faith is personal if it's to be real.
Make personal growth a daily priority.
Personal power is a feeling, like life.
Regrets are as personal as fingerprints.
Personal style is accepting who you are.
Your personal nature seeks its paradise.
On personal integrity hangs humanity's fate.
Every man's disease is his personal property.
Keeping a diary supports personal development.
My personal philosophy of life is one of ethics.
The greatest fulfillment, personal development.
